</head>

<body>
    <div id="dropdown" onclick="openclosenav()">
        <!-- Icon made by Freepik from www.flaticon.com -->
        <img id="dropdown-img" src="/imgs/dropdown.png" alt="dropdown menu">
    </div>
    <header id="tocollapse">
        <nav>
            <div id="brand">
                <strong>HC</strong>
            </div>
            <div id="menu">
                <ul>
                    <a href="#home" class="nav-items">
                        <li>Home</li>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#about" class="nav-items">
                        <li>About</li>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#features" class="nav-items">
                        <li>Features</li>
                    </a>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div id="login-reg">
                <ul>
                    <a href="/login"><button id="login-btn">Login</button></a>
                    <a href="/register"><button id="reg-btn">Register</button></a>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div id="goup">
            <a href="#home">
                <!-- Icon made by Pixel perfect from www.flaticon.com -->
                <img src="/imgs/up.png" alt="TOP">
            </a>
        </div>
        <section id="home">
            <h1>HamroChat</h1>
            <p>The only Chat app you'll ever need</p>
            <div id="down">
                <a href="#about">
                    <img src="/imgs/down.svg" alt="scroll down?">
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="about">
            <div class="content-heading">
                <h2>ABOUT</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="content-1">
                    <p>Made with utmost care, and keeping in mind of our valuable users, We bring to you HamroChat.
                        Our Chatting Application is like no other. It is simple, no fancy features, where you can have a 
                    one to one convo or a convo with a group!</p>
                    <!-- <p>Currently pursing my final year in Bachelors in Computer Science and Engineering, This project is
                        and will always be of great importance to me. The sole purpose of this creation of mine is to
                        bridge the gap between two individuals by means of communcation.</p> -->
                    <p>Popular chatting applications have group limit restrictions, and thus, we come to the resuce!
                        With a basic 1-1 chatting module, we even provide a group feature allowing you to connect with
                        over 1000 peers at a time! and we plan on adding more features, so 
                        <span class="tuned">Stay tuned!</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-2">
                    <img src="/imgs/saly.svg" alt="Saly on computer">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="features">
            <div class="content-heading">
                <h2>FEATURES</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="content content-wrap">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">SECURE</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <!-- <img src="/imgs/secure.svg" alt="secure"> -->
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p>Security is what we all yearn for. Thus, You can login/register with your google account, or our
                        secure login. You can rest assure your data will be safe and sound with us.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">CHAT</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <!-- <img src="/imgs/message.svg" alt="message"> -->
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-message"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p>We make communication easy and simple. From your part of the world, to any part of the world, It
                        is possible and absolutely for free.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">USER FRIENDLY UI</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <!-- <img src="/imgs/chill.svg" alt="chill"> -->
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-baby"></i>
                        <!-- <i class="fa-regular fa-face-grin-beam"></i> -->
                    </div>
                    <p>Built with great care and keeping in mind the tiniest details, so you can navgiate through the
                        website hassle
                        free. Take a chill pill, and enjoy!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">COLOUR BLIND FRIENDLY</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <!-- <img src="/imgs/chill.svg" alt="chill"> -->
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i>
                    </div>
                    <p>We don't want anyone to feel left out! And voila, you can tap the brush icon on the bottom
                        left corner of your scree, and we become compatible for all users!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>Made with â™¥</p>
